overview.en: A Decentralized, Intelligent Multi-level Digital Currency Service Platform.MunCB integrates multi-service modules with different levels and depths, such as real-time sharing of digital currency-related data, intelligent investment strategy supply, and digital asset investment escrow.
overview.zh: 去中心化、智能多層級的數字貨幣服務平台。系統集成數字貨幣相關數據實時共享、智能化投資策略供給、數字資產的投資托管等不同層級不同深度的多元服務模塊
